             was indicted for <rs id="t17811017-34-off162" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17811017-34-off162" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17811017-34-off162" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing a linen handkerchief, value 2 d. a pair of corderoy breeches, value 1 s. a pair of cloth breeches, value 1 s. a beaver coat, value 1 s. a blanket, value 1 s. a brown cloth coat, value 2 s. a waistcoat, value 1 s. a printed linen gown, value 1 s. and a piece of painted floor-cloth, value 2 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17811017-34-victim325" type="victimName">
                     George 
                     Alder
                  <interp inst="t17811017-34-victim325" type="surname" value="Alder"></interp>
